---
title: Chilli Jam-Glazed Tofu Burger with Sesame Fries & Sriracha Mayo
description: Got a hunger for a burger but you’re looking for something veggalicious, we understand and that’s why you won’t go
wrong with a tofu pattie between two buns. There’s the chilli jam glaze to run over the tofu and sriracha mayo to
bring in those classic burger tastes. It’s also perfect for dipping sesame fries in!
